N\gg n
P(N,n)=\frac{N!}{(N-n)!}\approx N^{n}
\frac{N!}{(N-n)!}=\frac{N\left(N-1\right)\cdots\left(N-n+1\right)\left(N-n\right)!}{\left(N-n\right)!}=N(N-1)\cdots(N-n+1)=\prod_{i=0}^{n-1}\left(N-i\right)
